        </p>

        <div
            class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row mt-6 sm:mt-10 justify-center items-center gap-4"
        >
            <div class="relative">
                <div
                    id="movementArea"
                    class="bg-white absolute w-[20%] h-[5.2%] left-[43.5%] top-[13%] transition-all rounded-sm "
                >
                    <img
                        id="eyes"
                        alt="eyes"
